name: No More Of That Jazz
description:
Exclusive only to Rock Castle Originals.

Designed by Mike Elwell.

Printed using the latest 8 colour HP Z Series technology.

HP fade-resistant inks.

Silk finish.

Paper thickness: 200gsm.

Unframed.

No white printing border.

A3, A2, A1 sizes, minus 5mm trimmed from the edge.

Printed in the UK.

Printed to order, no storage.

Print will be delivered rolled inside a poster tube.

Please allow 5 - 10 working days for delivery.

Free delivery (UK only.)
